image_analysis.description: A photograph showing a small workspace or storage area, possibly inside a closet. There is a white desk with a white chair and a white wicker basket on top. Above the desk is a hanging rod and a shelf containing several white magazine-style file boxes. Some of the boxes have small labels. To the left of the desk are rolled-up materials, and to the right, a garment bag hangs from the rod.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot of a closet converted into an office or storage space.

notes: The labels on the white boxes are small and partially obscured by distance, but 'PARIS 2' and 'ZORRO' are legible. The footer text is a standard Bates stamp used in legal/oversight documentation.
